item.description:
John Hauschildt will share the green way to develop film.  That's right, develop film with safe household items such as coffee and vitamin C.  Makes that now-inexpensive Hasselblad even more enticing, don't it?

 

FYI:  Main Street Art is located at 75 Main Street, Newfields, NH.  If you are interested in purchasing a brown bag lunch from the Newfields Country Store (just down the street from MSA), call 603-773-5656 by 11:15 a.m. and your lunch will be ready for pick-up on your way to the Art Talk.
item.name: Art Talk at Main Street Art in Newfields: Caffenol Film Developer
